  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Dios Tatáy, yachachiway Palabraykita,
 Willasaj runasman kamachisqaykita./
 
[V2]
 /Prometeyki, Diosníy, Qanta qhatínaypaj.
 Tukuy kawsayniyta Qanllaman qopuyki./
 
[V3]
 /Chimpamuyki, Diosníy, yanaparillaway.
 Llakiy jamuwajtin, Qanlla sonqochaway./
 
[V4]
 /Sinch'i sayanaypaj Qanlla yanapaway.
 Kallpaykita qoway pruebas jamuwajtin./
 
</lyrics></song>